it.unibz.tsmodel.overlay
Interface OverlayAttribute

public interface OverlayAttribute

Author:
mreinstadler This interface must be implemented by each overlay attribute. Weka requires for an overlay attribute a name, a type and a value, which can be also ? if no value is available

getAttributeValue

java.lang.String getAttributeValue(java.sql.Timestamp timestamp,
                                   OverlayStrategy strategy)
Parameters:
timestamp - the timestamp of the required observation
strategy - the strategy used to calculate overlay values - either boolean values or real values
Returns:
the value of the overlay attribute. It can be numeric (if the type is numeric), nominal(if the type is nominal),... and finally ? if the value is not available

Returns:
